about

Our story

about

Our story

Samuki was born on the planet of Meta and has always dreamed of traveling to distant worlds, winning battles and to be the greatest warriers in the world.

When portals to other dimensions with hostile monsters began to appear in his home world, he was one of the first to defend his home planet. He decided to go on a raid alone to sweep the hostile territory.

A familiar blacksmith forged him a special armor from the rarest materials and made him the sharpest sword that does not lose strength.

Are you ready

to go with Samuki to an unknown land and walk with him all the way to victory?

location

RPG level

location

RPG level

The level is organized in the form of an island on which the main action takes place. The hero appears in the central location of the island, which is the starting point and the point of preservation.

The total area of the island
is 1.5 million square meters

mission

Gameplay

mission

Gameplay

The hero must run through all sections of the island to make a complete sweep of all monsters. The island is divided into 6 main locations + 1 conservation location.

After a complete sweep and killing of the level boss, the hero moves tothe next level of difficulty. There are 100 levels in total.

0 conservation location
0 main locations
0 levels in total

With each level, monsters get +10% more attack power, +10% more life level, and also at different levels there are monsters of different types that have increased characteristics a kind of location bosses, which can be more than 1.

Every 10 levels, a separate location with a mega boss appears, which the player will need a lot of time and a large skill level to kill.

profit

Levelling up a hero

For killing each monster, the hero gets the experience that is needed to improve the characteristics of the hero.

The maximum available hero level is 100, each level gives

+5% to life force

+5% strike force

+5% to mana/magic

Every 5 levels, the hero opens a new skill that can be used in battle or to improve of the current skills.

Every 15 levels, a new type of weapon appears in the game, which the player can find at one of the locations.

tool of killing

Weapon

tool of killing

Weapon

The sword is the main weapon of the hero, available from the very beginning, has a high attack speed, but a low level of damage. During the game, the player can find several types of swords that will differ in different characteristics and sets of power-ups.

A two - handed sword is a very slow and very powerful weapon that can kill some enemies with a single series of blows.

The wand - is a ranged weapon with medium speed and attack power. Each hit slows down the opponents. Possession of the staff allows the hero to master the teleportation skill instead of the standard evasion of a blow.

The mace - is a melee weapon with an average impact force and an average attack speed, allows you to attack a group of enemies at once (splash attack).

The shield - is a protective addition to the onehanded sword, reduces damage, and also allows you to block some simple blows, as well as stop combinations of attacks.

enchantment

magic

Attack magic - is a type of magic that is able to attack a single enemy, belongs to the type of fire magic, caste time is fast. In addition to damage, enemies receive a stun effect for 1 second

Mass attack magic - is a type of magic that is able to attack a group of enemies and throws them aside, refers to the type of lightning magic, caste time is slow.

Shackle magic - is a type of magic that stops enemies and prevents them from attacking for a certain amount of time.

Support magic - is a type of magic that summons an assistant who fights on the side of the hero for a certain amount of time.

Healing magic - is a type of magic that can restore a small amount of the hero's life.

Boost Magic - is a type of magic that increases the hero's attack speed and strength by 15 seconds.

statistic

tokenomics

Automatic
acquisition
of liquidity

The solution in this situation is to provide a liquidity pool within the smart contract itself, which is singled out as a separate function, immutable and able to automatically track the activity of all swaps and transactions.

To do this, the Zeus protocol uses a system of fees, 2.5% of which is always stored in a separate pool in the smart contract itself and is automatically converted into a liquidity pool upon reaching the threshold of 500 billion tokens (half of the issue).

Neither contract owners nor developers have access to the dedicated pool. As a consequence, the automatic liquidity pool is able to thwart almost any attempt to exert pressure from the market or swaps.

Token
distribution

The Zeus protocol uses a complex reward structure that requires no additional fees and is hosted within the smart contract itself. To work properly, distribution must occur without user involvement and additional costs.

The distribution of tokens is set at 2.5% and directly depends on market activity. As part of the distribution of the feature, exchanges, decentralized wallets, as well as wallets that have been seen in attempts to manipulate the market or dump tokens in large quantities are excluded from the reward system.

Burning

The Zeus protocol provides the combustion function as one of the regulation methods. Main reasons:

1. Reduce supply to maintain price.

2. Increase the value of the token.

3. Restrain the rise in cost. Sometimes it is necessary to reduce the price if the token has a high inflation rate.

Burning occurs by automatically sending 2.5% of tokens to a system address that no one has access to. The address is generated automatically and subsequently destroyed, the burning address is public and each user can check the transaction history.
